|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[to_timestamp(EventTime@1) ASC NULLS LAST, SearchPhrase@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true] |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[SearchPhrase@1 as SearchPhrase, EventTime@0 as EventTime]                                                      |
|               |         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                 |
